cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with data matching and merging, which is a common problem in databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of semantics and trust in the framework suggests an artificial intelligence (cs.AI) component. The evaluation of the framework on different datasets involves data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and machine learning techniques (cs.LG).
